                <h1>Recess Interviews: filmmaker Tom Whiteside</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/e776f85a-81e9-4bad-bd94-14a811651bd2.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="The&#x20;Devils&#x20;took&#x20;down&#x20;the&#x20;Florida&#x20;State&#x20;Seminoles,&#x20;previously&#x20;undefeated&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;ACC,&#x20;Saturday&#x20;at&#x20;Indoor&#x20;Cameron&#x20;Stadium" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            The Devils took down the Florida State Seminoles, previously undefeated in the ACC, Saturday at Indoor Cameron Stadium

